Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=10}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:02.73,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{The long battle of\N400 years had ended, - OG}Quatrocentos anos de luta\Nfinalmente chegaram ao fim,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:07.27,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{and all the citizens of Skypiea continued their joyous party day after day. - OG}e os Skypieans continuaram\Nsua celebração por dias a fio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:12.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu... Eu... Não consigo beber mais...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ali estão eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:24.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:28.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami, acorda todo mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:36.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos roubar o ouro e fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem ouro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Idiot! Not so loud! - OG}Idiota! Fala baixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:45.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean "idiot"?!\NYou're louder than I am! - OG}Como assim "idiota"?!\NVocê está mais alto que eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:48.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! I'm louder, you say?! You're the louder one! - OG}Mais alto que você?!\NVocê é que tá gritando!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:54.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What?! You're calling me loud\Nwhen you're really super loud?! - OG}O quê?! Está me chamando de barulhenta\Nquando você está gritando mais ainda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:58.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Your voice is the one that's\Nreally super-mega-ultra loud! - OG}É a sua voz que é\Nsuper-mega-ultra alta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:02.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's no way that's true! I'm\Ntalking loud because you're loud! - OG}De jeito nenhum! Só estou falando\Nalto porque você está gritando!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're the one who spoke loud first! - OG}Você gritou primeiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Calem a boca! Não consigo dormir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:07.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What?! You're the loud one! - OG}E daí?! Você continua sendo a barulhenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It wasn't me! It was you! - OG}Não sou eu! É você!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:13.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm a delicate woman! I wouldn't yell\Nwith my mouth wide open, would I?! - OG}Sou uma dama delicada! Eu não gritaria\Ncom a boca escancarada, não é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:16.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Viu? Viu?! Sua boca está escancarada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é porque você me irritou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:22.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/q2]Like I said, you don't have to shout, you know! - OG}{\q2}Acabei de dizer que não precisa gritar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.80,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami! Bom dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.22,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh? Ainda não é de manhã!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Usopp me bateu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:13.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8/q2]There's no way I'd do something like that! - OG}{\an8\q2}Eu nunca faria isso!
Comment: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:13.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8\q2}There's no way I'd do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8][untranslated?] - OG}{\an8}Não me acuse disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:17.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]But you did hit me here! - OG}{\an8}Mas você me bateu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Here! It's really true! - OG}{\an8}Bem aqui, eu senti!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:21.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]Yeah, yeah... Go ahead and\Nbe feeble-minded like that. - OG}{\an8}É, é... Continua dizendo\Nisso pra si mesmo, idiota.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]What do you mean, "feeble-minded"?! - OG}{\an8}Como assim, "idiota"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:16.80,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Caramba, acorda, dorminhoco!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O pessoal do Blue Sea gosta\Nmesmo de festejar, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:28.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É o quarto dia seguido.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Their vitality isn't normal. - OG}A disposição deles é incrível.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então, esse é o plano.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:42.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo, pessoal! Não é sempre que\Na gente visita uma ilha do céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Make it so that you'll have no regrets! - OG}Garantam que não vão\Nembora com arrependimentos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chefe! Encontramos o sino dourado!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, está falando sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:59.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim. Está preso no\NGiant Jack caído.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos puxando agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:04.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Those who can help, come to the western seashore! - OG}Se puder ajudar,\Nvenha até a costa oeste!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hurry! Hurry up! - OG}Rápido! Andem logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Okay, guys! Gather everyone! - OG}Certo! Juntem todo mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The belfry was found! - OG}Encontraram o sino!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{At the western seashore. - OG}Na costa oeste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:15.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Okay! - OG}– Ok!\N– Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:16.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem certeza?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! Hurry! - OG}É! Anda logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They said they found the bell that fell in the sea! - OG}Parece que caiu no mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:24.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Those who can move, gather at the western seashore! - OG}Sim. Quem puder se mover,\Nvá até a costa oeste!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The belfry was found! - OG}Encontraram o sino!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's at the western seashore! - OG}Está na costa oeste!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:32.84,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{The belfry was? - OG}O sino...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mais uma vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:38.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um, dois...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:42.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Puxem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! We still need more people. - OG}Droga! Ainda não temos\Ngente suficiente.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's the pride of our ancestors' city, Shandia. - OG}Este é o orgulho dos\Nnossos ancestrais—de Shandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We'll get it at any cost! - OG}Faremos o que for preciso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Give it everything you got! - OG}Deem tudo de si!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:17.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mais uma vez! Um, dois...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Pull harder! - OG}Puxem com toda a força!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:55.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Rubber band?! So you\Ncall this a rubber band?! - OG}Elástico?! Isso é\Nchamado de elástico?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:06:01.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{My Usopp Rubber Band did 90% of\Nthe work of taking Giant Jack down! - OG}{\q2}Os Elásticos da Perdição do Usopp fizeram\N90 por cento do estrago no Giant Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Uau!\N– Uau! Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm the only one in the\Nworld that has them. - OG}E eu sou o único\Nno mundo que tem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Uau!\N– Uau! Demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:15.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But... put that aside for now. I'd\Nlike to show you this iron sheet! - OG}Mas... vamos deixar isso de lado.\NAcheguen-se pra ver esta chapa de ferro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:20.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora, senhoras e senhores!\NEsta não é uma chapa de ferro qualquer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:26.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I tore it off from the Going Merry, our\Nship that endured very hard travels - OG}É uma chapa de ferro tirada do nosso navio,\No Going Merry, que sobreviveu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:29.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{on the Grand Line, as well as Enel's attacks! It's the "King of Iron Sheets"! - OG}{\q2}à Grand Line e aos ataques de Enel!\NÉ a "Rainha das Chapas de Ferro"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How about it?! You\Nguys want iron, right? - OG}E aí?!\NVocês querem ferro, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Would you trade me dials for this? - OG}Querem trocar alguns dials por isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não! Eu quero esse elástico!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu troco por esse elástico!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I want one, too! Is that okay?! - OG}Eu também quero! Posso ter um?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]Me, too! - OG}{\an8}Eu também!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.17,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Uau... Eles estão falando sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]Give me one, too! - OG}{\an8}Me dá um também!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]Me, too! - OG}{\an8}Eu também!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Conchas! Consegui conchas! Isso aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:05.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sorte, sorte! Que sorte a minha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're in a good mood,\Naren't you, Usopp? - OG}Você está de muito bom humor, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:05.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did the negotiation go well? - OG}A troca deu certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ouviu isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I got lots of dials! - OG}Consegui um monte de dials!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I press it and... - OG}É só apertar aqui, e...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just like that! - OG}sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom pra você.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:19.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom pra mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:22.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{With this many dials, I can\Ndo many different things! - OG}Com tantos dials,\Nposso fazer todo tipo de coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:27.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The Usopp factory'll\Nbe running full steam! - OG}A Fábrica Usopp vai\Nfuncionar a todo vapor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:32.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Zoro, if you make your swords Flavor Swords - OG}{and store the smell of\Nstuff like melons in them, - OG}{\q2}Ei, Zoro! E se eu fizesse suas espadas\Nvirarem espadas com aroma de melão?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{you can enjoy your everyday training! - OG}Isso ia animar\Nseu treino diário!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:36.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não, obrigado.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:41.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah! I can make\NNami's Clima-Tact stronger! - OG}Ah, é! Posso melhorar\No Climate Baton da Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{My slingshot will be incredible, too! - OG}E meu estilingue vai\Nficar melhor do que nunca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:51.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E onde estão Robin,\NLuffy e os outros?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:55.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Luffy and the others are still\Ninside. Robin went somewhere. - OG}Luffy e os outros ainda estão lá dentro.\NRobin foi pra algum lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:04.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In any case... this\Nsnake's really conked out. - OG}Olha só... Essa cobra\Nrealmente tem um sono pesado.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He kept dancing day after day... - OG}Ela ficou dançando por dias...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:10.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{though I don't know what\Nhe was so happy about. - OG}Imagino por que estava tão feliz.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Anyhow, they'd better come out soon, - OG}De qualquer forma, eles deviam\Nsair logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{because if he wakes up, he could\Ngive them a hard time again. - OG}Pode dar problema se ela acordar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This good-tempered snake? - OG}Essa cobra tão boazinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:21.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Idiot! You just don't know\Nhow troublesome he can be! - OG}Idiota! Você não sabe\No problema que ela pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This good-tempered snake? - OG}Essa cobra tão boazinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:28.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Like I said, you can be so\Noptimistic because you didn't see - OG}{what a pain this snake can be. - OG}Como eu disse, você não viu\Ncomo essa cobra ficou brava.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This good-tempered snake? - OG}Essa cobra tão boazinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:33.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, now listen here, Usopp! - OG}Tá, chega, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This good-tempered snake? - OG}Essa cobra tão boazinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It was a Tone Dial! - OG}Era um tone dial!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:39.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't do stupid stuff like that! - OG}Chega dessa piada idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:44.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 1150)}É, é idiota! Muito idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:47.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que isso?!\NO que essa cobra come?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Já chegamos, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:50.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Look! There they are! - OG}Olha! Ali está!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uau! Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É de verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:57.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's pretty! It looks just like the ones\Nthat we saw at the monkeys' house! - OG}Que lindo! Igual aos que\Nvimos na casa dos macacos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Viu? Viu? Viu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:02.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's all this! - OG}Olha tudo isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:06.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não é demais?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So this is gold... - OG}Então este é o dourado...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Que bonito...\N– Incrível...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Eu não esperava que fosse tão...\N– Que magnífico.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:25.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But one of the side\Ncolumns has been broken. - OG}Mas uma das colunas\Nlaterais está quebrada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, but there isn't much we can do. - OG}É, passou por muita coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:30.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Look at that. - OG}Ei! Olha ali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:34.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então este é... o poneglyph...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:39.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The stone that our ancestors\Nrisked the city's life to protect...! - OG}A pedra que nossos ancestrais\Narriscaram a cidade pra proteger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just what is written on it, Chief? - OG}E o que está escrito nela, Chefe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Something we're better\Noff not knowing... - OG}Não cabe a nós saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós apenas...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:55.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{"Hold our true motive in your\Nhearts and speak not of it. - OG}"Guarde a verdade em seu coração,\Ne não fale sobre ela.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:59.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Somos nós que tecemos a história...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{with the sounding of\Nthe grand belfry..." - OG}com o soar do grande sino..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:06.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como você sabe essas palavras?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:09.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estavam gravadas nas\Nruínas Shandianas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:13.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So you were the keepers,\Nentrusted with this for generations. - OG}{So you were the guardians,\Nentrusted with this for generations. - Gord, Viz}Então vocês eram os guardiões que\Nprotegeram isso por gerações.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:23.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Could it be... You can\Nread those characters?! - OG}Será que... Você consegue\Nler esses símbolos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:32.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Poseidon, the "ancient\Nweapon" named after a God... - OG}Poseidon, a arma antiga\Ncom nome de um deus...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Its whereabouts... - OG}Sua localização...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?! O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She said "ancient"! - OG}"Antiga"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arma antiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why is it talking about\Nsomething like that?! - OG}Por que escreveriam\Nalgo assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:46.58,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Outra arma... diferente\Nda Pluton que li em Alabasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.21,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{To think that there are\Nsuch dangerous things - OG}Pensar que coisas tão perigosas
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:52.59,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{in this world waiting to be found...! - OG}ainda dormem em algum lugar\Ndo mundo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just as I thought, this\Nwas a disappointment. - OG}Eu deveria ter imaginado.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.35,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{This isn't what I want to know. - OG}Isso não é o que estou procurando.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:00.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! - OG}Ei, você!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:03.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Aren't those the same\Nkind of characters - OG}{on that engraving next to it?! - OG}Não tem mais daqueles símbolos\Ngravados ao lado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:12.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Gol D. Roger"...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What?! - OG}O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.45,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu cheguei aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:22.66,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I will guide this text to\Nthe ends of the earth. - OG}Vou guiar este texto até\Nos confins do mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.41,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Pirata Gol D. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:28.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{King of the Pirates...! - OG}O Rei dos Piratas...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:33.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso quer dizer que ele veio\Na esta ilha do céu também?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:39.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No, more importantly, why\Ncan he use these characters? - OG}Não, mais importante,\Ncomo ele conhecia esta escrita?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:43.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So it says Roger? - OG}Eu ouvi "Roger"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:45.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você o conhece?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:51.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's a Blue Sea pirate who came to\Nthis sky more than 20 years ago. - OG}Ele é um pirata do Blue Sea que veio\Na este céu há mais de vinte anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então o nome dele está gravado ali?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:54.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:59.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't know how he reached this bell, - OG}Eu não sei como\Nele chegou a este sino...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but this sure is indelible\Nproof that he did. - OG}mas esta é a prova definitiva de que ele chegou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:08.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, there're\Ntwo kinds of Poneglyph stones. - OG}Pensando bem, existem\Ndois tipos de poneglyph.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:13.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ones with information, and others\Nthat indicate their whereabouts. - OG}Os com informações\Ne outros que marcam localizações.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:16.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And this stone is one of\Nthe ones with information. - OG}Este é do tipo com informações.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.35,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,"Eu cheguei aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:28.48,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I will guide this\Ntext to the ends of the earth." - OG}Vou guiar este texto até\Nos confins do mundo."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.94,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Guiar este texto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.78,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Guiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It couldn't be...! - OG}Será que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Será que o Rio Poneglyph é...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:48.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chefe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:53.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Este poneglyph já\Ncumpriu seu papel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cumpriu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:57.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's right. - OG}Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:02.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I bet those Poneglyphs\Nwith information - OG}{scattered around the world - OG}Acredito que os poneglyphs informativos\Nespalhados pelo mundo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:08.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{will, when put together,\Nbecome one text - OG}{that will fill the "Blank\NHistory" for the first time. - OG}podem ser combinados num único texto\Nque preencherá o Século Vazio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:14.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In other words, the text\Ncompleted by connecting them... - OG}Em outras palavras, conectar\No texto completo cria...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:19.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That is the Rio Poneglyph,\Nwhich still does not exist. - OG}algo nunca visto antes:\No Rio Poneglyph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Gol D. Roger, Rei dos Piratas,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:26.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{definitely delivered this\Ntext to its destination. - OG}deve ter entregue este\Ntexto ao seu destino.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:34.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então não é mais...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:43.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós... não precisamos mais...\Nlutar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:50.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I see... Our ancestors' wish\Nhas been fulfilled, then? - OG}Entendo... Então o desejo dos\Nnossos ancestrais foi cumprido?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:53.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Chefe!\N– Chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:59.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom... Bom... Então nosso\Ndever foi cumprido!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.95,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,O que significa que eu também
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:09.50,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{have to guide the text on those\NPoneglyphs that I read in the past... - OG}tenho que guiar o texto dos\Nponeglyphs que li...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:14.00,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{to the end of the Grand\NLine... to Laugh Tale... - OG}até o fim da\NGrand Line... até Laugh Tale...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:24.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Young lady, the feeling that straw hat\Nkid gives me is reminiscent of Roger. - OG}Moça, aquele garoto do chapéu de palha me dá\Na mesma sensação que Roger dava.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is it my imagination? - OG}Mas talvez seja só minha imaginação.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O nome dele é Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{My interest in him never fades. - OG}Ele nunca deixa de me interessar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:36.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{D? I see. He's got the\Nsame letter in his name. - OG}D? Entendo. Então eles compartilham\Nessa letra em seus nomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:44.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes... and I'm sure it's a big issue\Nthat has something to do with history. - OG}Sim... e tenho certeza de que é bastante\Nimportante para nossa história.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:46.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{By the way, young lady... - OG}A propósito, moça...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You guys wanted gold, right? - OG}Vocês queriam ouro, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You said it's more valuable\Nthan Vearth in the Blue Sea. - OG}Você disse que é mais valioso\Nque vearth no Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:54.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:57.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How about taking the\Nbroken belfry column, - OG}Já que não podemos dar o sino,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{though we can't give you the bell... - OG}que tal a coluna do sino?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Boa ideia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:05.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Naturally, we have to show our\Nappreciation to you guys somehow. - OG}Temos que mostrar nossa gratidão\Na vocês de alguma forma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:05.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:06.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't hold back! - OG}Nós insistimos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:09.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem certeza?! Eles vão\Nficar felizes de ouvir isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:11.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! - OG}Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:17.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então tá! Vamos levar\Nisso pro pessoal do Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:19.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wrap it with cloths! It's hard to carry! - OG}Embrulhem com pano! É difícil de carregar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We'll give this to those\Nwho saved our land! - OG}Vamos dar pro pessoal\Nque salvou nossa terra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:23.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Caramba, isso é enorme...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:35.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que a Robin está fazendo? Ela está atrasada!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Darn! I'm hungry! - OG}Ai, cara! Estou com fome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:43.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In any case, this place is so empty. What's going on? - OG}Este lugar esvaziou rápido.\NO que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:47.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Where the heck did the\Nguerrillas and angels go? - OG}Pra onde foram todos\Nos guerrilheiros e anjos?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:51.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, it's better they aren't here. If\Nthey find us, they'll chase us around! - OG}Bom, melhor que não estejam aqui.\NVão nos perseguir se descobrirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:56.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Since we're trying to steal\Nthis much gold and run, - OG}Estamos prestes a roubar\Ntodo esse ouro e fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{they won't just let us go! - OG}Eles não vão simplesmente nos deixar escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:01.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, Nami and Conis are preparing\Nto set sail, but we still have to hurry. - OG}Nami e Conis estão preparando\No navio, mas ainda temos que correr.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Before that, Sanji, do you\Nhave something to eat? - OG}Antes disso, Sanji, temos\Nalgo pra comer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Not until we get to the ship. - OG}Sim, no navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:09.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But you've gotta have\Nsomething to munch on, right? - OG}Mas você deve ter\Num lanchinho pra beliscar, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]Give me some! - OG}Me dá!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]I can't give you what I\Ndon't have! Just give up! - OG}Não posso dar o que\Nnão tenho! Desiste!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Que saco!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{We don't have to wait\Nfor that woman, do we? - OG}Não precisamos esperar\Naquela mulher, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu vou na frente\Ne embarcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Idiota! Não vai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Moss Head Idiot! - OG}Idiota Cabeça de Musgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Idiot Moss Head! - OG}Cabeça de Musgo idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:24.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you go into the forest alone, you won't make it three steps without getting lost! - Wtf - Villager}Você não dá três passos sozinho\Nnaquela floresta sem se perder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, olha! É a Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yoo-hoo, Robin! - OG}Ei, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:40.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hurry! Hurry up! We've gotta\Nrun! We stole some gold! - OG}Rápido, rápido! Corre!\NRoubamos ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Idiot! Don't say that! - OG}Cala a boca, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:43.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Take a good look behind her! - OG}Olha atrás dela!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're all coming back here together! - OG}Estão todos voltando de uma vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's tons of them! - OG}Tem um monte deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:56.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é ruim! Isso é ruim!\NIsso é muito ruim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E o que é aquilo? Um canhão enorme?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's gotta be it! - OG}Tem que ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:03.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They all came back all at once! - OG}Voltaram todos de uma vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rápido pro navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:08.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We can no longer stay here! - OG}Não podemos ficar aqui mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:11.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Check this out! We got a good catch! - OG}Olha isso! Conseguimos um bom saque!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A mochila está cheia! Somos ricos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:17.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hm? They all have bags on their back! - OG}O quê? Todos estão com suas mochilas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:20.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me... Are\Nthey already leaving?! - OG}Não me diga... eles já\Nestão indo embora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:22.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, parem, pessoal! Parem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:25.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{See?! They found us out! - OG}Viu?! Nos pegaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:26.48,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ei! Parem! Parem, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll strike a pose and say it! - OG}Hora de fazer uma pose\Ne discursar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:34.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You guys say, "Stop! Stop!" but... - OG}Vocês podem pedir pra parar o quanto quiserem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É! Manda ver, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:41.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós arriscamos nossas vidas pra vir\Naté esta ilha do céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.50,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:44.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And we've found the\Nlegendary city of gold! - OG}E encontramos a\Nlendária Cidade do Ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:46.09,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]Robin-chan! Hurry up! We'll be caught! - OG}{\an8}Robin! Anda logo! Vão nos pegar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:49.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How the heck can we, proud pirates,\Njust go back empty-handed?! - OG}Vocês realmente esperam que piratas orgulhosos\Ncomo nós voltem de mãos vazias?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Pegar?!\NDo que ele está falando?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:54.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Só queremos agradecer a eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:58.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei moça, vocês não vão\Nlevar esse ouro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:02.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Looks like they don't need it! - OG}Acho que não!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah não!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:14.07,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Ei! Espera!\N– Ei! Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:17.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're all after us! It's scary! - OG}Estão todos atrás de nós! Que medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E aí?! Fui legal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É! Mandou bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Robin-chan! Hurry! - OG}Robin meu amor! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:29.76,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Ei! Voltem!\N– Ei! Voltem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:35.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Continuem correndo até\No fim do céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:39.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=11}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=14}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
